title: Valar Rereadis: TWOIAF - The Freehold of Valyria
description:
With the excellent JoeMagician joining us, we discuss the early days of Valyria. The look, government, worship, their natural resources including volcanos, dragons and a myriad of fun blood and fire influenced topics.

JoeMagician: https://www.youtube.com/c/JoeMagician
Ashaya's Survey: bit.ly/arlens
